query:
SELECT
                date_trunc($1, start_at AT TIME ZONE $5) AS date,
                CAST(SUM(seconds) AS float) / CAST(60 AS float) / CAST(60 AS float) AS hours
            FROM
                tasks
            WHERE
                user_id = $2
                AND start_at AT TIME ZONE $5 >= $3
                AND start_at AT TIME ZONE $5 <= $4
            GROUP BY
                date
            ORDER BY
                date ASC;
